筨字的康熙字典解释

【未集上】【竹字部】　筨； 康熙笔画：13； 页码：页885第14
【廣韻】【集韻】?胡南切，音含。筨?，竹實中者。【戴凱之·竹譜】筨?竹，大如脚指，堅厚脩直，腹中白膜闌隔，狀如濕麪生衣。將成竹而笋皮未落，輒有細蟲齧之。隕籜之後，蟲齧處往往成赤文，頗似繡畫。南康所出。　【集韻】或作䈄、?、笒。

Bamboo, as big as toes, thick and straight, with an albuginea septum in the abdomen, like a wet robe. The bamboo will become a bamboo but the skin of the bamboo shoot has not fallen off, and there are small insects biting it. After the meteorite, the insect bite often becomes a red text, which looks like an embroidered painting. Produced by Nankang.　【Jiyun】Or as qu,?, 笒.
